Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,While the old man was \Nwatching the horse races
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:07.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,on TV and checking his payout tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:11.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,we found a dark horse payout \Nticket he didn't recall buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:15.71,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe when he dropped his wallet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:19.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,he picked up someone else's \Nticket and put it in his wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I could've accidentally added another digit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:26.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,All right, tonight we're having \Nsushi for dinner, sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:29.55,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to Beika Irohazushi next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:33.42,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So the elated old man dragged \Nus to Beika Irohazushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,the restaurant next to the detective agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,where we met an unfamiliar employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I don't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you new?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:44.56,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.31,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Wakita Kanenori, a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:51.69,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the type of guy to \Nsettle down in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:54.06,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I eventually ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.68,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what you'd call a drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:01.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,As we finished eating and \Nwere settling our bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:05.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,a woman ran into the restaurant, claiming her \Npouch had been stolen from her on a full train.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:10.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Using the GPS on the phone in her pouch,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,she tracked it down to Irohazushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:16.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the timing, apparently someone \Nin the restaurant was the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:17.59,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:22.01,Suzuyo,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Hijirisawa Suzuyo (47) \NVictim of Theft
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.45,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just how much was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:23.31,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}None of the money in my wallet was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Then who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:28.52,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But the ticket I had with my cash is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:31.02,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,My dark horse payout ticket \Nworth a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:32.53,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.17,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:36.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:41.19,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the ticket you picked \Nup belongs to that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.22,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.79,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:47.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It was stolen about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:51.67,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the races \Nin my office around then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:57.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But the TV broadcast of the races \Nended about 50 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:01.68,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were out buying tickets, \Nyou only saw the last race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:07.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,An little over an hour ago, you \Nwould've been near the ticket booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:09.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:13.67,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the thief was in a \Nrush to redeem the ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.90,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,ran into you, and dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:23.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And you picked it up and \Nput it in your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:27.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:32.21,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Kogoro-san, didn't \Nyou have a winning dark horse ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.46,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:37.01,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we make this a contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.01,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,A contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:45.39,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see which of us can \Nfind the thief first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:51.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,B-But there wasn't any \Nblood on anyone's sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make this an unsolvable case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.19,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.36,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.70,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange that that woman's \Nblood wasn't on anyone's sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:12.33,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But why did the thief leave the \Nstolen pouch in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.71,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A professional thief \Nwould've taken the money
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:20.97,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and left the incriminating \Nwallet in a nearby trashcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.18,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So why did they bring it into Irohazushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.90,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Feel that bright morning sunlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday is when the love and cases start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A chef and the old man \Nhave a detective showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.98,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Who hid the dark horse payout ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:42.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:28.97,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(404,1)}The Tokyo-Style Detective Show Next Door \N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:27.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"The Tokyo-Style Detective \NShow Next Door, Part Two!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:32.47,Irohazushi,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Irohazushi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.75,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Since the stolen pouch was \Nleft in this bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.98,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,is there some significance \Nspecific to Irohazushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:43.98,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Or would any sushi restaurant have worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:48.48,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's that young man's first \Ntime at this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:54.66,Tsunetaka,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Harashima Tsunetaka (25) \NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.22,DCItalic,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll have the nigiri special, \Nsome chawanmushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.66,DCItalic,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And a cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:55.87,DCItalic,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.65,DCItalic,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.07,DCItalic,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:02.60,DCItalic,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom's back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:03.88,DCItalic,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:09.84,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The man sitting next to him \Nseems to have been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.31,DCItalic,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,The regular nigiri and an oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:19.98,Tameshige,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Munechika Tameshige (42) \NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:20.02,DCItalic,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Also, do you have the limited availability \Nseasonal grilled fish today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:26.42,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And that woman seems to be a regular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.62,DCItalic,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.12,DCItalic,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.60,DCItalic,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,And what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.54,DCItalic,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.06,DCItalic,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the regular guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.25,DCItalic,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,He got hurt in a traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:49.68,Natsume,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Ashino Natsume (33) \NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.70,DCItalic,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:47.53,DCItalic,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In that case, I'd like a \Nhighball and seafood chirashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.96,DCItalic,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Extra sea urchin, salmon roe, and wasabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:50.59,DCItalic,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.22,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:58.73,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Waiter, I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.72,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:05.82,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't this guy show me his sleeves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.12,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.03,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a suspect, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.54,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.18,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.41,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough nonsense out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:21.82,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,The great Mori Kogoro would \Nnever stoop to stealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.84,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sir. Show her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.40,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Prove you're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.84,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Stains on your sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.10,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:36.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just happened to spill some \Nsoy sauce on myself earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's more soy sauce colored \Nthan blood colored, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.53,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.88,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It even smells like soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.98,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,But it sounds like he's making excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.53,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, seriously. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.93,DCItalic,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's not totally innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.89,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.78,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Just confess already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.82,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:03.21,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Who stole my pouch on the train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.71,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even take the train today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.81,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I walked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.47,DCMain,MUKECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I took the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.61,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like full trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.92,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,I took a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.72,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the base fare \Nfrom my office to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:24.98,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.73,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It was careless of me to celebrate my \Ndark horse payout ticket on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.49,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I was willing to forgive \Nyou if you came clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.99,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'll have to go through the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.52,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure you'd prefer \Nto get the police involved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.75,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,so you can erase all doubt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.69,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Involved... and erase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.75,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:57.29,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,The police will only have \Nto search your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.26,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:03.77,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,the person who has either \Na million yen in cash
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:08.82,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,or the stolen dark horse \Nticket on them is the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:17.28,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's no need to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.54,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,The thief's already a \Ncarp on a cutting board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:27.29,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is for me to name \Nthem and for them to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.31,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,N-Name the thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.86,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you know who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:36.55,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:39.90,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I know who stole your pouch on the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:43.32,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,brazenly came to eat \Nsushi at this restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:49.56,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,and hid that pouch in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.24,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must have figured that out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.74,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Figured what out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:03.62,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,When my pouch was stolen,\NI grabbed the thief's sleeve
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.83,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,with my finger wrapped in \Na bloodstained band-aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:12.63,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason that blood \Nwasn't on anyone's sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.76,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:20.72,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,The thief passed through this restaurant's \Nshop curtains to erase that blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:26.70,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure Kogoro-san has \Nalready figured that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.98,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the mystery \Nsolving to the professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:36.36,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see one of your detective shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.86,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:47.00,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? So the Sleeping \NKogoro's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:54.70,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot about food \Nwhile working as a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.25,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.68,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.76,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why they put \Nginger in ginger fried pork?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.43,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:07.49,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because it's \Ncalled ginger fried pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.77,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because it tastes better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.07,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.85,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger breaks down proteins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:20.45,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,They put it in to soften the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.53,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,And protein is found in blood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.54,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to wash \Nbloodstains out of clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.79,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,because the proteins in \Nthem stick to the fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:35.16,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,If you wash bloodstained \Nclothes with ginger juice,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.73,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,the stains will come right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.17,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll try it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.68,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Doesn't that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.66,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:48.18,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,We serve thinly sliced ginger \Npickled in sweet vinegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.69,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,So the man who ordered a \Nmountain of pickled ginger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.94,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:02.30,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,When you went to the bathroom to hide \Nthe pouch hidden in your jacket,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:07.95,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you pour the juice from the pickled \Nginger on your sleeve to wash out the stain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.82,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.12,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously didn't steal anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.37,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.44,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:20.15,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you wanted to leave because \Nthere's a show you want to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.38,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:27.18,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro-san and his family came after \Nthe horse races ended just after four.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:33.69,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,This woman barged in here \Nabout an hour later at five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:39.83,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to leave after \Nthe argument about the theft,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.19,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,so that would've been around 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:47.45,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,If you walked here, it probably takes \Nyou less than thirty minutes to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:52.95,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,The only shows on around that \Ntime are cartoons and kids shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:59.18,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wanted... to see a kid's show...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.19,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kamen Yaiba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.97,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy boss's adviser is supposed \Nto be on today's episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.47,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kamen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.35,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.80,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,And you're so into it, you \Ndon't want to miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.27,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,This Kamen Whatever show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.98,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.39,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't know exactly how it works,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:26.11,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,but wouldn't my sleeve be the color of pickled \Nginger if I poured its juice on my sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:30.42,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure the color would come \Nout if I washed it right after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.24,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.70,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Then go ahead and search my belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.96,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a million yen or \Na dark horse payout ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.88,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You guys show them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.42,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll know who the thief is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.49,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.42,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.11,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.48,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:50.43,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that old!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.86,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Just show them what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:57.07,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have the \Nticket, you're innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.82,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:05.36,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I know who has the dark horse payout ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.57,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.96,Irohazushi,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,1)}Beika Irohazushi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:16.96,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.75,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.80,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.77,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, let me see your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:29.12,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,My dad ran into someone at the ticket booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.93,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,He accidentally put a ticket that \Nwas on the ground in his wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.54,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.78,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.19,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.36,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.57,Ticket,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Yamanaka 9 Race \NWin \N8 Pirate's Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.32,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.57,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,This is a win ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:46.52,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:52.18,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I bet five thousand on a quinella \Nticket for first and second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:54.83,Ticket2,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(710,1)}Yamanaka 9 Race \NQuinella \NN8-11
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.83,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Its payout is two-hundredfold, \Nso it's worth a million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.29,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't mislead people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.97,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.83,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.71,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:04.96,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.04,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,We're not finished—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.48,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.83,DCMain,HARASHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm leaving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:09.30,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.05,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.14,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:12.92,DCMain,ASHINO,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.05,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.61,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.00,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Calm down, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.91,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The dark horse payout ticket \Nwas a quinella ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.49,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:41.12,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said you like mysteries, \NI thought I'd see what you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:45.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But you still have a lot of \Nlearn, detective drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.12,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:49.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger does contain protease,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.63,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,an enzyme that breaks down proteins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:56.14,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But ginger isn't the only \Nthing they're found in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's also found in radishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:03.10,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If you wrap grated ginger in a handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.15,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,gently pat the front and \Nback of a bloodstain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and then place a tissue over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,the blood will transfer to the tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat the process three or four times,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.62,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and the bloodstain disappears completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And unlike pickled ginger, \Nit doesn't leave any color.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.47,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you did inside the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:23.83,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:28.68,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The man who ordered the grilled fish, \Nwhich always comes with grated radish,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:38.42,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe he happened to see it on the \Nmenu and wanted some grilled fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:42.10,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dish sushi restaurants rarely serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, when he ordered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:50.53,DCItalic,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Also, do you have the limited availability \Nseasonal grilled fish today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.58,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,He asked about the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:57.03,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It proves he's been here before \Nand knows you serve grilled fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:17:00.82,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And only an amateur
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:04.37,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,would bring a stolen pouch all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,One who never imagined the victim would
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,use their phone's GPS to \Ntrack him all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.64,DCItalic,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Who stole my pouch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.47,DCItalic,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I know the thief is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:25.03,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you come here to remove \Nthe bloodstain on your sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:29.05,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You could've returned home and taken \Noff your shirt or thrown it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.11,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Because he had something to do after this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.61,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,that didn't allow him to have \Na bloodstain on his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:40.71,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That young man with the TV \Nshow he doesn't want to miss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:45.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and the woman who wants to go home \Nto participate in online auctions...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.63,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,would have no problem with a \Nbloodstain on their sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.86,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But not so for that \Nbespectacled man on his way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:55.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,to meet someone for drinks \Nat an expensive restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.83,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he's meeting his in-laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:03.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,who are so strict he's too \Nnervous to eat around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:08.65,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what they'd say if he \Nshowed up with blood on his sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:14.46,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that doesn't prove I'm the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:18.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've already confessed that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.48,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I haven't admitted to anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:24.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You said you came by bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you take the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.08,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't like full trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Surely there are empty trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:35.32,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,B-But she was riding in a full... train...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:41.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know the train \Nshe was in was full?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.53,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were on that train, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.73,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.82,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.08,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a rich guy like \Nyou on his way to drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.34,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,at an expensive restaurant steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.91,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's my wife's parents who are rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:13.14,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,My wife wanted for nothing \Ngrowing up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.50,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Her spending habits haven't changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.92,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't afford it on my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.66,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,My savings have been \Ndrained, and I'm in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:25.48,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,While I was wondering \Nif I should borrow money
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.93,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,from her parents that I'm about to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.44,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.60,DCItalic,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.69,DCItalic,FRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Won what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.06,DCItalic,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,My dark horse payout ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.44,DCItalic,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.83,DCItalic,FRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.65,DCItalic,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:43.32,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,So I acted without thinking \Nout of desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.32,DCItalic,FRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then you're paying for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.20,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I gave in to temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.80,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.22,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.12,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.62,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:14.30,DCMain,HIJIRISAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.18,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.82,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:23.99,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant we're at has \Na vintage Romanée-Conti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.19,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,Can I treat my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.17,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.00,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.00,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.92,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Have a beer and come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:40.20,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also, I need to go see the police now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.76,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be going to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.26,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.93,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What do you mean, the po—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:50.40,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should've said that from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:55.12,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I know I just stole from someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.44,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like a weight's \Nbeen lifted off my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.32,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually never bought \Na payout ticket before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:07.09,DCMain,MUNECHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea where or how \Nto exchange it for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:11.83,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty minutes later, the police \Narrived at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:18.72,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Munechika-san was taken away with \Nthe slightly cheerful expression
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:21.18,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,of a man who's just finished a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:49.59,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated you, Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:52.80,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:54.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.64,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:03.44,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a discount on your sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:06.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.96,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's got another apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:12.39,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:15.95,Police,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Beika City Fifth Street Police Box
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really have to turn it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:19.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going to claim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:20.84,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:27.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's going to claim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:28.73,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:31.72,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:32.48,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:37.98,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The old man turned over his dark \Nhorse payout ticket to a police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:42.58,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta turn in lost items.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:24:08.96,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,General, the tiger is afraid \Nof me and won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:53.74,DCMain,WAKASA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:56.24,DCMain,WAKASA,0000,0000,0000,,The folding screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:02.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tie him up and put him on display!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:06.22,DCMain,HANNO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:14.97,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,The Woman With White Hands \N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:13.94,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "The \NWoman With White Hands, Part One!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:33.03,DCMain,WAKITA,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:34.99,Wakasa,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Wakasa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:34.99,Hint,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Wakasa-sensei's House
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:34.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wakasa-sensei's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:39.99,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.33,0:24:36.21,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My dark horse payout ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.21,0:24:38.03,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Instead of betting on horses, \Nmake some money doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.03,0:24:39.44,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nice one, Ran-neechan.
